content.rendered:
A hygienic way to keep bed surfaces clean between patient uses.

50m long Rolls

  • Beautiful Soft to Touch Paper Bed Sheet Roll
  • 59cm wide, 2 Ply, sheets.
  • White Embossed
  • Perforated sheet for easy tear.
  • Carton of 6 Rolls
  • White.

These bedrolls are perforated paper rolls for bed protection. Logiroll consists of a 2-ply, micro embossed, glued tissue to create a durable and plush surface protection layer. Logiroll can be used as surface protection in a range of clinical situations such as protection for examination couches, stretcher sheet, first aid room bed cover and trolley covers.
